Question: What is the air quality forecast for Bangkok today?
Call: { "func_call": "get_air_quality_index", "location": "Bangkok", "severity": "moderate" }
Response: { "alerts": [{ "type": "Air Quality", "severity": "Unhealthy", "message": "AQI is 168. Sensitive groups should avoid outdoor activities. General public may experience minor irritation.", "expires": "2024-05-22T09:00:00Z" }] }

